if you want to run tests of yar, please follow these steps:
1. cp htdocs folders to your DocumentRoot
2. config yar.inc, change the defination of API_HOST to the URL, which is point to the htdocs folder under DocumentRoot, please becareful, if you miss the last slash, Webserver will response 302 redirect
3. then make test

Simple example:
1. set: YAR_API_URI to / in tests/yar.inc
2. run: php -d extension=modules/yar.so -S localhost:8090 -t tests/htdocs
3. then run: make test
